about.summary: Python implementation of standards from The InternationalAssociation for the Properties of Water and Steam

name: iapws
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.4" %}

package:
  name: iapws
  version: {{version}}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/iapws/iapws-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3d7a7a17343157dacd3f654b7f82d1974492209756c4de99332d4f6b375227e6

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
    - scipy
  run:
    - python
    - scipy

test:
  imports:
    - iapws

about:
  home: https://github.com/jjgomera/iapws
  license: GPL-3.0
  summary: 'Python implementation of standards from The InternationalAssociation for the Properties of Water and Steam'
  license_family: GPL3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tntmatthews
